{"tid":2513413,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"SpaceX堅韌號艙成功搭載四名太空人返回地球","createTime":"2021-05-02T13:14:29.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-02T14:35:18.000Z","uid":3873,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"e9aac72bf9ca53267cf09bb56cb3a66abbffc00f","tid":2513413,"uid":3873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T13:14:29.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://cablenews.i-cable.com/ci/news/article/37/733531?utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_campaign=share\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcablenews.i-cable.com%2Fci%2Fnews%2Farticle%2F37%2F733531%3Futm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_campaign%3Dshare&d=LCDPOb8M8FyYKm9nuxOGtSC3g8rst4cc2NZsp7q1N1o%3D&h=5807283c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcablenews.i-cable.com%2Fci%2Fnews%2Farticle%2F37%2F733531%3Futm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_campaign%3Dshare&h=b14ad46a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://cablenews.i-cable.com/ci/news/article/37/733531?utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_campaign=share</a><br />\n<br />\n美國民營企業SpaceX研發的載人飛船，搭載四名太空人由太空站返回地球，是飛船執行正式任務以來首次成功返航，亦是美國自1968年以來首次夜間降落。<br />\n<br />\nSpaceX控制中心人員在語音通話說：「<span class=\"red\">歡迎返回地球，感謝選擇乘搭SpaceX，若已加入飛行獎賞計劃，這一程你已賺取6800萬里數。</span>」堅韌號太空人霍普金斯回答：「我們已返回地球，並會接收這些里數，可以轉讓嗎？」<br />\n<br />\n4位太空人在國際太空站分別進行了太空漫步，微重力影響人類心臟的科學實驗，以及嘗試在太空種植蔬果。167天任務期刷新了由美國升空，逗留太空的最長紀錄。"},{"pid":"d6ab2f73378b44220e8cbc1a0a576ea85bef28d9","tid":2513413,"uid":77355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T13:16:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58e4a7a5d8643ea382c1e13032fb2bd784a3469a","tid":2513413,"uid":108337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T14:26:52.000Z","msg":"好幽默<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c41db792f7965108b917d22525b6d9a17e36545c","tid":2513413,"ui